tform,pipeline management,sales intelligence\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"ClientEra\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://clientera.aio/legal/terms\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Terms of Service | Client Era\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Terms governing the use of Client Era services.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://clientera.aio/legal/terms\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"ClientEra — The Unified Commercial OS\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"One platform for your entire commercial relationship — from the first conversation to the last payment.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.clientera/logo.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?603d046c9a6fdfbb\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/logo.png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/logo.png\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,400&amp;family=Geist:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><main style=\"background:var(--navy);min-height:100vh;color:var(--text);display:flex;flex-direction:column\"><header style=\"width:100%;padding:24px clamp(24px, 5vw, 64px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);background:rgba(11,22,40,0.85)\"><a style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;text-decoration:none\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/logo.png\" alt=\"Client Era Logo\" width=\"120\" height=\"32\" style=\"object-fit:contain\"/></a><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px\"><a style=\"color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px\" href=\"/legal\">Legal Center</a><a class=\"lh-btn\" style=\"padding:8px 16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:8px;color:var(--text);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s\" href=\"/\">Return to Site</a><style>\n          .lh-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important; }\n        </style></div></header><div style=\"flex:1;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px 24px;width:100%\"><article class=\"legal-content\"><h1>Client Era Terms of Service</h1>\n<p><strong>Last Updated: March 2026</strong></p>\n<p>These Terms of Service (&quot;Terms&quot;) govern your organization&#39;s access to and use of the Client Era B2B sales operations and distributor management platform (&quot;Service&quot;). By accessing or using our Service, you agree to these Terms on behalf of your organization.</p>\n<h2>1. Access and Accounts</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Authorized Users:</strong> Access is strictly limited to authorized personnel (e.g., distributors, sales managers, fulfillment teams) designated by the subscribing organization.</li>\n<li><strong>Security:</strong> You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials. Client Era is not liable for unauthorized access stemming from compromised internal credentials.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2. Acceptable Use</h2>\n<p>You agree not to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use the Service to transmit malicious code, malware, or illegal content.</li>\n<li>Attempt to bypass our security features, rate limits, or access controls.</li>\n<li>Use the platform to infringe on the intellectual property of third parties.</li>\n<li>Reverse-engineer, decompile, or otherwise attempt to extract the source code of the Client Era platform.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3. Platform Reliability and Availability</h2>\n<p>Client Era guarantees a 99.9% uptime SLA for enterprise customers as detailed in your specific Master Services Agreement (MSA). However, we are not liable for downtime caused by factors outside our control (e.g., major cloud provider outages, ISP failures).</p>\n<h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Client Era Rights:</strong> The Client Era platform, including its software, algorithms, UI/UX designs, and trademarks, is the exclusive property of Client Era.</li>\n<li><strong>Your Data:</strong> You retain full ownership of all transaction data, distributor records, and operational information uploaded to the platform. You grant Client Era a limited license to process this data solely for the purpose of providing the Service.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>5. Financial Transactions</h2>\n<p>Client Era facilitates operational workflows (e.g., Proforma invoices, SORs). <strong>Client Era does not act as a payment gateway or process funds.</strong> All final financial settlements occur outside the platform between the respective business entities.</p>\n<h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>\n<p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, Client Era shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages (including loss of profits or operational delays) arising from the use of the Service.</p>\n<h2>7. Governing Law</h2>\n<p>These Terms shall be governed by the laws applicable in the jurisdiction defined in your primary Master Services Agreement, without regard to conflict of law principles.</p>\n<p>Contact <strong><a href=\"mailto:legal@clientera.com\">legal@clientera.com</a></strong> for questions regarding these Terms.</p>\n</article></div><footer class=\"ce-footer\"><div class=\"ce-footer-grid\"><div><div class=\"ce-footer-logo\">client<em>era</em></div><p class=\"ce-footer-desc\">The AI-Powered Commercial Operating System. One timeline. One truth. Zero gaps.</p><p style=\"font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:14px\">Built for India. Compliant worldwide.</p></div><div><div class=\"ce-fc-h\">Platform</div><ul class=\"ce-fc-links\"><li><a href=\"/sales-ops\">Sales Ops</a></li><li><a href=\"/sales-management\">Management</a></li><li><a href=\"/customer-support\">Customer Support</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Field Sales</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Desk Sales</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Operations</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Distributor Portal</a></li></ul></div><div><div class=\"ce-fc-h\">Company</div><ul class=\"ce-fc-links\"><li><a href=\"#\">About</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Security</a></li><li><a href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Pricing</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Careers</a></li><li><a href=\"#\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><div class=\"ce-fc-h\">Legal</div><ul class=\"ce-fc-links\"><li><a href=\"/legal\">Legal Center</a></li><li><a href=\"/legal/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href=\"/legal/terms\">Terms of Service</a></li><li><a href=\"/legal/cookies\">Cookie Policy</a></li><li><button style=\"background:none;border:none;padding:0;color:inherit;font:inherit;cursor:pointer;text-align:left\">Cookie Preferences</button></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"ce-footer-bottom\"><span>© 2026 ClientEra. All rights reserved.</span><div class=\"ce-footer-links-row\"><a href=\"/legal/privacy\">Privacy</a><a href=\"/legal/terms\">Terms</a><a href=\"/legal/cookies\">Cookies</a></div></div></footer></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-4c9e6c08dcc7a301.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7121,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[4581,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[9351,[\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-ec2df61e02bf9503.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[484,[],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n7:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\na:I[484,[],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\nc:I[484,[],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\ne:I[7123,[],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/53ebd3f615d9682f.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"